dataCsv.Site_Description: The Nightingale is somewhat intact. The sides are collapsedâ€“the ports side collapsed outward and the starboard side collapsed inward. The stern is upright but disconnected from the sides. All of the machinery is gone including the windlass, any winches, and anchors.
